<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Interaction_design&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Academic Institutions specializing in Interaction Design">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Academic Institutions specializing in Interaction Design</span></h2>
